  <body>
    <front><contents /></front>
    <chapter>
      <heading>
        Software documentation for the TTIOTransportClient
        class
      </heading>
      <class name="TTIOTransportClient" super="NSObject">
        <declared>TTIOTransportClient.h</declared>
        <desc>
          <p>
            <em>Inherits From:</em> NSObject
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>Conforms To:</em> NSObject (NSObject)
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>Declared In:</em> Transport/TTIOTransportClient.h
          </p>
          <p>
            WebSocket client that connects to a
            <code>TTIOTransportServer</code>, sends a JSON
            query, and collects the resulting transport packets.
            Built on libwebsockets (
            <code>libwebsockets-dev</code> package). The client
            runs a private libwebsockets service loop inside
            <code>
              <ref type="method" id="-fetchPacketsWithFilters:timeout:error:">-fetchPacketsWithFilters:timeout:error:</ref>
            </code>
            and blocks until the server emits EndOfStream or the
            connection closes.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Cross-language equivalents:</strong>
            <br /> Python:
            <code>ttio.transport.client.TransportClient</code>
            <br /> Java:
            <code>
              global.thalion.ttio.transport.TransportClient
            </code>
          </p>
        </desc>
        <method type="NSArray&lt;TTIOTransportPacketRecord*&gt;*">
          <sel>fetchPacketsWithFilters:</sel>
          <arg type="NSDictionary&lt;NSString*,id&gt;*">filters</arg>
          <sel>timeout:</sel>
          <arg type="NSTimeInterval">timeoutSeconds</arg>
          <sel>error:</sel>
          <arg type="NSError**">error</arg>
          <desc>
            <em>Description forthcoming.</em>
          </desc>
        </method>
        <method type="instancetype">
          <sel>initWithURL:</sel>
          <arg type="NSString*">url</arg>
          <desc>
            ``url`` must be a ``ws://`` URL (``wss://`` is not
            yet supported).
          </desc>
        </method>
        <method type="BOOL">
          <sel>streamToFilePath:</sel>
          <arg type="NSString*">outputPath</arg>
          <sel>filters:</sel>
          <arg type="NSDictionary&lt;NSString*,id&gt;*">filters</arg>
          <sel>error:</sel>
          <arg type="NSError**">error</arg>
          <desc>
            Streams a filtered dataset into a new
            <code>.tio</code> file. Scope: HDF5 provider;
            FLOAT64 / Compression.NONE wire encoding (same as
            the offline codec). @param <var>outputPath</var>
            Destination <code>.tio</code> path. @param
            <var>filters</var> Filter dictionary; pass
            <code>nil</code> for a full stream. @param
            <var>error</var> Out-parameter populated on failure.
            @return <code>YES</code> on success.
          </desc>
        </method>
      </class>
    </chapter>
  </body>
